Does Bei know about this?

678
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:48,260
That's why I came to you today.

679
00:34:49,740 --> 00:34:50,900
I hope you won't tell him.

680
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:52,860
I don't want him to know any of this.

681
00:34:53,490 --> 00:34:54,860
Ever since we got together,

682
00:34:54,860 --> 00:34:56,050
I haven't done those things.

683
00:34:58,780 --> 00:34:59,620
Okay.

684
00:35:00,340 --> 00:35:01,380
Got it.

685
00:35:02,610 --> 00:35:04,340
No way I'd make the one I love

686
00:35:04,740 --> 00:35:07,210
