692
00:35:20,890 --> 00:35:22,380
Stop joking. I'm serious.

693
00:35:23,770 --> 00:35:24,620
How do you know

694
00:35:24,620 --> 00:35:25,900
Bei would never cheat?

695
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,340
My friend tested him.

696
00:35:28,340 --> 00:35:29,180
Huh?

697
00:35:30,570 --> 00:35:31,610
A dozen girls sent over.

698
00:35:31,780 --> 00:35:32,740
He never wavered.

699
00:35:33,300 --> 00:35:34,610
A dozen?

700
00:35:34,990 --> 00:35:35,870
That's why I'm sure

701
00:35:35,890 --> 00:35:37,170
