704
00:35:43,690 --> 00:35:45,900
Bei's a tough man. Solid as a rock.

705
00:35:46,010 --> 00:35:47,210
A hot reserved type.

706
00:35:49,490 --> 00:35:50,690
(Are you sleeping?)

707
00:35:57,700 --> 00:36:00,820
(Voice Call)

708
00:36:09,860 --> 00:36:13,220
(Daily Chocolate)

709
00:36:20,210 --> 00:36:21,050
(Xiaoxi,)

710
