713
00:36:27,530 --> 00:36:28,530
Thank you for meeting me.

714
00:36:29,490 --> 00:36:30,330
I'm leaving now.

715
00:36:30,810 --> 00:36:31,650
Mm.

716
00:36:31,650 --> 00:36:32,860
Go ahead, Jiang Yifan.

717
00:36:34,570 --> 00:36:36,260
She promised to stay with me one night.

718
00:36:36,860 --> 00:36:38,610
An hour, a minute, or a second missing

719
00:36:38,610 --> 00:36:39,460
