720
00:36:40,050 --> 00:36:42,010
I'll wait here for her till sunrise.

721
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:48,980
♪Waiting for my destiny's signal♪

722
00:36:52,300 --> 00:36:53,690
(Hi, I'm Yuan Qian.)

723
