738
00:37:27,600 --> 00:37:30,199
♪I'll admit♪

739
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:34,239
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

740
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:38,986
♪There's nothing that I wouldn't try to do♪

741
00:37:39,011 --> 00:37:43,199
♪For this feeling to have you♪

742
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:45,679
♪I'll resist♪

743
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,014
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

744
00:37:48,039 --> 00:37:50,199
♪Your touches again♪

745
00:37:51,080 --> 00:37:55,060
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

746
00:37:55,085 --> 00:37:58,119
♪For an image of you♪

747
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:01,559
♪Take my hand again♪

748
00:38:01,560 --> 00:38:03,319
♪Take my mind again♪

749
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:06,759
♪Break into my heart again♪

750
00:38:07,160 --> 00:38:09,337
♪I'm falling out again♪

751
00:38:09,362 --> 00:38:11,199
♪I'm on my knees again♪

752
00:38:11,200 --> 00:38:15,039
♪To beg for the truth♪

753
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:21,039
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

754
00:38:21,040 --> 00:38:26,039
♪Is that the secret to love♪

755
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:29,359
♪I thought it had came from below us♪

756
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:32,839
♪Did it come from above♪

757
00:38:32,920 --> 00:38:36,679
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

758
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:41,999
♪Is that the secret to love♪

759
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:44,839
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing,♪

760
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:49,279
♪this secret of love♪
